structure.unit: COUNTIES, CITIES, AND OTHER LOCAL UNITS

law.history: Repealed 1982 Ky. Acts ch. 434, sec. 15, effective July 15, 1982. -- Created 1956 Ky. Acts ch. 25, sec. 4, effective May 18, 1956.

metadata.catchline-at-repeal: City legislative body may create administrative department for administration of public parks and recreational activites in second-class cities.
